<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>New KYC Submission</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      background: #ffffff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      text-align: start;
      margin: auto;
    }
    h2 {
      color: #1e90ff;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    p {
      color: #333333;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .kyc-status {
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #1e90ff;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #777777;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>New KYC Submission</h2>
    <p>Hello Admin,</p>
    <p>A new KYC submission has been made by <strong>{{name}}</strong>.</p>
    <p><strong>KYC Status:</strong> <span class="kyc-status">Pending</span></p>
    <p>Please review and approve or reject the submission.</p>
    <br />
    <p class="footer">Best regards,<br>Your Team</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
